name: UnChillStablyRealOut
description:
UnChillStablyRealOut

This is my new favorite merged model, using equal parts:

  • ChilloutMix

  • Project Unreal Engine 5

  • StablyDiffused's Magnum Opus

They give me fantastic results on a wide range of people and styles, and since I'm using it for my creations, I wanted to share it with you.

All of the credit in the world goes to the creators of the three models above, I just mashed them together.

(I should mention that if any of the previous authors would like me to take this down for whatever reason, I'm happy to do so.)
